subject: Track and Field
Olympic Games (2008)
lead_paragraph: Ethiopia’s Tirunesh Dibaba completed a historic double, winning the 5,000 in 15 minutes 41.40 seconds and becoming the first woman to win the 5,000 and 10,000 in the same Games.
